TopicTitle: What Does This ksp.log Error Mean?

Articles.Content:
It's a simple mod (Cargo Bay, with two animated doors).  I've put Mesh Colliders on the main Body and each door; all three pieces have the Mesh Collider convex flag set.

What/Where should I be looking to resolve this err?  Is it an unset flag/value in Unity?  Is it something in my modeling program (Blender)?  Sometimes, this works fine.  Then not.

The part compiled correctly in the Unity Editor without errors.  Imported from Blender to Unity via an FBX file; animation (single) was baked.
